title: One dead as Saudi Arabia shoots down missiles from Yemen
text:
One dead as Saudi Arabia shoots down missiles from Yemen 4:46am EDT - 00:46 
One man has died in Riyadh after Yemen's Houthi militia fired seven missiles that were shot down over Saudi Arabia. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
